Name: Mighty Planes
Title: Ilyushin IL-76
Desc: Volga-Dnepr's Ilyushin-76 delivers equipment to a remote mine in Nunavut.
LongDescription: Baffinland Mines needs to get equipment to a remote mine in Nunavut to support shipping operations for the summer and have hired one of Volga-Dnepr's Ilyushin-76.
